# Environment variables for this project.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed.
# No environment variables are required for local execution with the default local DVC remote.

# To use a cloud DVC remote, set the appropriate credentials.
# AWS S3 example:
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key_id
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret_access_key
# AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=us-east-1

# Google Drive example (requires dvc[gdrive]):
# GDRIVE_CREDENTIALS_DATA=<base64 encoded service account JSON>
